  <brief_title>A Phase 3, Double-Blind 2 Arm Study in the Treatment of Acne Vulgaris</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase 3, Multi-Center, Randomized, Double-Blind, Vehicle-Controlled, 2 Arm, Parallel Group Study Comparing the Safety and Efficacy of IDP-123 Lotion and IDP-123 Vehicle Lotion in the Treatment of Acne Vulgaris</official_title>
